<h1>Help & Support</h1>

<section class="help-section">
    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>Welcome to our Volunteer Management System! Follow these steps to get
        started:</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Register:</strong> Create an account using your email and a
            password.</li>
        <li><strong>Complete Your Profile:</strong> Fill out your profile with
            your personal information, skills, and availability.</li>
        <li><strong>Explore Events:</strong> Browse through available events and
            volunteer opportunities.</li>
        <li><strong>Get Matched:</strong> Our system will match you with events
            that suit your profile.</li>
        <li><strong>Participate:</strong> Join events and make a difference in
            your community!</li>
    </ol>
</section>

