    <div class="faq">
        <h3>Can I update my profile information?</h3>
        <p>Yes, you can update your profile information at any time by logging
            into your account and navigating to the "Profile" section.</ p>

            <h3>How do I contact the support team?</h3>
            <p>If you need assistance, you can contact our support team via the
                contact information provided on the Contact page.</p>

            <h3>How do I find events to volunteer for?</h3>
            <p>Once you complete your profile, you can browse and apply for
                events in the "Events" section of our platform.</p>
        </div>
